Solutions_from_Data.csv
Description:
This file contains the results of 9 SQL queries providing data-driven recommendations to the Head of Sales for improving dealership profitability, inventory decisions and expansion strategy.

Key metrics included:

Top makes and models to prioritise in inventory

States with the highest revenue potential

Optimal mileage range for highest selling price

Best sellers to partner with (highest profit margins)

Body types to stock based on recent trends

Recommended price range per make

Condition tier vs profit margin

Transmission type growing in demand

Best manufacturing years to stock

Use this file for: Section 3 of your Looker Studio dashboard (Solutions — Green charts)
